rows.name:
The energy filling the cores has dropped!
Not by much, but it's something![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33440110_MSG0030
rows.name:
I think it's Void himself that's gotten weaker,
and it's showing in his connection to the cores.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33440110_MSG0040
rows.name: I see... It must be the effect of the spear.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33440110_MSG0050
rows.name: We need this to work. Let's activate the other one as well.[ST:wait ]
